{"tid":1856900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主人隔離期間愛貓慘遭活埋行先一步","createTime":"2020-02-02T01:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T02:58:50.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88fb0f1666e56efdd08fa82a1893c21ab6454fbf","tid":1856900,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T01:33:39.000Z","msg":"根據大陸傳媒報道，事件1月30日在江蘇無錫發生，貓主正接受隔離觀察，尚未被確診是否患上武漢肺炎。他的愛貓「啾咪」當時被隔離在家中露台，主人亦已安排朋友帶走。但社區人員卻以消毒為名，在未通知貓主的情況下，將貓咪活埋殺死。事件在微博及豆瓣流傳，有疑似是受害主人與社區書記的對話流出，當中書記直認貓咪已被「深埋土裏」，更對主人說「你的心情我理解，但是在疫情方面請你理解」。<br />\n<br />\n早於1月26日，博客「蜘蛛猴面包」亦曾在武漢拍攝短片，當中訪問一位在武漢寵物店的女士，她亦復述有人把貓從武漢以正規渠道辦理檢疫坐火車帶回家，但回到家那邊的居委會說「要把她們家的貓活埋」，短片並沒透露是那個省市的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200202/GMYRJF2HABM7OHGOYGPQUQ2QWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200202%2FGMYRJF2HABM7OHGOYGPQUQ2QWU%2F&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=ec60bbc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200202%2FGMYRJF2HABM7OHGOYGPQUQ2QWU%2F&h=e8cf98ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200202/GMYRJF2HABM7OHGOYGPQUQ2QWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200202/large/1580574906_2db4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200202%2Flarge%2F1580574906_2db4.jpg&h=3bee089a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸醫師根本殺病人，估計好快團聚"},{"pid":"a9ca17a7494fc413ead8115e11563fefed5c23ad","tid":1856900,"uid":315545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貓貓"},{"pid":"134dbb04293cae3d10dbb66d44e2d9cd835